_sText:
This is the finished version of the gg_e_rave_trance_beta. I have added a 3d skybox, a few props, and changed a few lighting details. Thanks to uberkirsche for the rotating disco light prefab, and thanks to Dirge for building advice. 

The fps is not great on this map but I have tried to improve it as much as possible by applying the no-draw texture to every brush side that cannot be seen, and then turning most of the brushes into func_detail. I don't know what else I can do.
